  by 209.66.108.5 with SMTP; 28 Jun 2002 01:36:34 -0000
Received: (qmail 22735 invoked by uid 97); 28 Jun 2002 01:36:45 -0000
Delivered-To: qmlist-jakarta-archive-lucene-user@jakarta.apache.org
Received: (qmail 22684 invoked by uid 97); 28 Jun 2002 01:36:44 -0000
